rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0002
rows.name: How come we're low on food?

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0003
rows.name:
Like, aren't you the Boss round here?
Couldn't you just tax 'em a little?

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0004
rows.name:
I'd hate to see you in power!
Life is hard here, Hikari.

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0005
rows.name:
Aletta's in the hinterlands of Iira.
The population is small compared
to the capital.

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0006
rows.name:
With the resistance forces coming in
such large numbers, resources are
strained. There's no preparing for it.

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0007
rows.name:
I can't really force them to provide
for us. And anyhow, taking care of
ourselves is the right thing to do.

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0008
rows.name: Makes sense, I guess. A little.

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0009
rows.name:
We'll all need to start doing our bit
from now on to try to ease the
food supply problem.

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0010
rows.name:
That's right. It's the only way
we'll be able to manage.

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0011
rows.name:
Hey, Adel-sama! If there's anything
you need me and Sata to do, then just
holler and we'll do it!

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0012
rows.name:
I mean, it's not right for us to just
freeload. We want to earn our keep!

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0013
rows.name:
Haha... Thanks everyone.
I think we're going to be just fine.
